Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要開開關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.31,0:01:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.94,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螢幕有什麼變化？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有顯示了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D14在閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的螢幕如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M15在亮著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.66,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒鋼彈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.70,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,口袋裡的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.31,0:02:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需工具、渣古的部件及武器 這三樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工具買就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部件呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去偷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做小偷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆的殘骸在這衛星殖民地到處都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那裡找能用的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在尋寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有被聯邦捉到的危險的呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到存放武器的地方去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝有武器的貨櫃車還剩兩台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米舍遺留的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被聯邦士兵拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩有一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在停車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個貨櫃車已停了三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想查就請便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢！不要留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是寄放的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道 知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,號碼是租用車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查查停車時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼 我有好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天前就停在這沒動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！看看裡面吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍從這個衛星殖民地滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩 你做什麼？住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！喂！住手，住手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還我爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們殺了我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.88,0:04:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為聯邦軍在這裡建造基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了戰爭 爸爸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還我爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你的心情我是很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這是吉翁軍不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以以後不要再做這種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.12,0:04:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一把電磁斧 爆裂炮12發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大收穫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹的好 亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要扔了這輛貨櫃車 還得去弄一台新車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武器不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有特別的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.58,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在還沒接近鋼彈之前就會被打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能偷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就有點困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼好主意就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到好主意了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！很厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,講給我聽聽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒殺他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏過去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用這些發煙筒及氣球去設陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點就選靠近聯邦基地的森林較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那就不用擔心會使人捲入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來要怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鋼彈引來 施以突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話用電磁斧也能贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易的吧 這下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}難道你不曉得自己很甜美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:52.90,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.41,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊！讓我來愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.41,0:07:01.94,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh Let me love you so
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抬頭望天空雖遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.56,0:07:15.96,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる空は遠いけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.36,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但有無盡的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.36,0:07:22.67,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない夢がある
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是的  從被創造的世界裡  逃出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:33.67,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ　創られた世界の中を　抜け出して
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想成為自由之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:38.78,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}自由になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.09,0:07:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直不斷奔跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.09,0:07:45.29,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.29,0:07:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能來到天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.29,0:07:52.10,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我將化為一陣風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.41,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.81,0:08:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為我相信會如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.81,0:08:02.34,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.84,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我永不放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.84,0:08:07.94,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.25,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每個人都說如此就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.25,0:08:17.25,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}これでいいのと誰もが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然沈默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:24.87,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無口になってしまうけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是的 希望瞭解未曾遇到的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:39.58,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ  今まで出會えなかった  本當の愛を知りたいの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.28,0:08:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸長著手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.28,0:08:47.09,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}腕を伸ばして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.09,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能觸及天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.09,0:08:53.65,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:09:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你將會看到一個嶄新的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:09:04.34,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい始まりの時  見えるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你永不放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:11.94,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭喪著臉嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天你爸爸不是要回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能跟你一起作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有要幫忙的事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰的事我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明天的任務是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能將這個包裹送一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要送到那裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磁片裡面有指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果作戰失敗 我死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了那個磁片 照我的命令行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的工作 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼死了之後？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是萬一之時的防備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能不會使用到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天2點 打倒鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會成功地保護這衛星殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過個好耶誕節啊 亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼不會死吧！會贏吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的 交給我了 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 巴尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊！請實現我的願望！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓決不再搗蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的 我發誓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後不再在街上玩 直接回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不再把蛇或蜥蜴放在女生桌內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以 請你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你保佑巴尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.60,0:11:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請解救這衛星殖民地以及大家的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是出擊的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢！亞爾 媽媽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讓你們久等不好意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離船很近的地方 發生戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透過窗戶看到吉翁的船被擊沈的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這也差一點就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向聯邦軍投降的吉翁艦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然好像裝有核子武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然載有核子武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照聯邦的調查原是想基亞的路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又會到這中立的殖民地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾怎麼了？亞爾不是在這下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要再打仗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要阻止巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渣古 接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在三分鐘後就和本基地接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"艾螢克斯"的彈藥餘量狀況如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手還剩五百發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,研究所來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕支援行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克其中尉 出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.01,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不追來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩台都往夏貝區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克其中尉 撤回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在原地作戰比較有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏貝區是無人地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林和它作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉！撤回！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.93,0:15:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼，快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用再戰了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴尼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克其中尉怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著 只是昏過去了而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在渣古的人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被轟得亂七八糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比絞肉還慘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 不要緊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！要不要緊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔架 快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.75,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要緊吧！喂！孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.87,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 聽好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.27,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個包裹裡有我錄的證言錄影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有證據文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何這個衛星殖民地會成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核子飛彈的目標？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡我所知的都說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一我死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這個交給警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如大人們相信這是真的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個衛星殖民地我想就會得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本想直接去警察局去自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢？那樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得在逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒不作戰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己會變得不像自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是恨聯邦 也不是要替隊長他們的報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法表達的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和它 想跟鋼彈它打一仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我是士兵的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由連我自己也不很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 我大概會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為此事憎恨聯邦士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們也只是和我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是做他們認為該做的事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要怨恨他人或責怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我最後的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果運氣好活了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且戰爭結束之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會回到這衛星殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣分別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了！亞爾 健康的生活啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.71,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向克莉絲問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.83,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才在喊叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八點半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是好天氣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.95,0:20:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像神在慶祝新學期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我找不到毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也真是的 你想把廚房弄得到處是水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.11,0:21:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！借用一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子的爹 等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是沒辦法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾差不多該出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不走會遲到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手帕帶了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成大人了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像比較穩重了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.09,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要轉任到地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟你道別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然的消息 嚇到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原想和巴尼打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能由亞爾轉達一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.80,0:22:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說："多謝他對我的關照！"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.02,0:22:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 巴尼也一定會覺得很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.73,0:22:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.68,0:23:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 亞爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.58,0:23:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見！克莉絲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.08,0:23:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫長痛苦的戰爭終於結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.19,0:23:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平日子到來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.69,0:23:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這衛星殖民地裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.69,0:23:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭也留下了很深的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是只是失去了校舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也失去了許多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母 兄弟以及友人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.91,0:23:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個和平是由許多人的犧性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.21,0:23:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所換來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.61,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們不要忘記這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.82,0:23:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你們長大成人之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 哪裡在痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.55,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再掀起這樣的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.31,0:23:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了世界的和平 希望你們能努力奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.53,0:23:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫老師等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.47,0:24:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們活下來的人所承擔的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.47,0:24:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾， 要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.37,0:24:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭馬上會再開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定是更、更誇張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.17,0:24:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且又好玩又大的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.88,0:24:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對嘛 然後不只是彈殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以撿實彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.88,0:24:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許還能撿到軍隊的槍呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.10,0:25:48.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噓をついた夜には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.81,0:25:54.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.30,0:26:00.30,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧嘩をしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.60,0:26:08.30,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.60,0:26:15.10,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.30,0:26:21.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.00,0:26:29.30,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.00,0:26:35.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.20,0:26:41.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.90,0:26:47.61,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃
